 "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015462, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Praise be to God who answers me whenever I call Him, even though I am sluggish when He calls upon me. And praise be to God who grants me whatever I ask for even though I am stingy when He asks me for a loan. And praise be to God Who honored me by taking charge of my affairs, instead of leaving my affairs to others who may humiliate me. And praise be to God Who endeared me although He is needless of me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ANTAL HAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE AD-O’O-HO FE-YOJEE-BONEE WA IN KUNTO BATEE-AN HEENA YAD-O’O-NEE WAL-HAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE AS-ALO-HU FA-YO’TEE-NEE WA IN KUNTO BAKHEE-LAN HEENA YAS-TAQRE ZONEE WAL-HAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE WA KALA-NEE ILAIY-HE FA-AKRA-MANEE WA LAM YAKIL-NEE ILAN NAASE FA-YOHEE-NOONEE WAL-HAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE TA-HABBAB ILAIY-YA WA HAWA GHANIY-YOON A’NNEE.", "ArabicText1": "اَنْتَ الْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِيْ اَدْعُوْهُ فِيُجِيْبُنِيْ وَاِنْ كُنْتُ بَطِيْئًا حِيْنَ يَدْعُوْنِيْ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِيْ اَسْئَلُهٗ فَيُعْطِيْنِيْ وَاِنْ كُنْتُ بَخِيْلًا حِيْنَ يَسْتَقْرِضُنِيْ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِيْ وَكَلَنِيْ اِلَيْهِ فَاَكْرَمَنِيْ وَلَمْ يَكِلْنِيْ اِلَى النَّاسِ فَيُهِيْنُوْنِيْ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِيْ تَحَبَّبَ اِلَيَّ وَهُوَ غَنِيٌّ عَنِّيْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGre